com.ulflander.model
Class Token

java.lang.Object
  com.ulflander.model.Text
      com.ulflander.model.Token

public class Token
extends Text

A token is the most tiny part of a document: a word, a number, and so on. A token has a type (word, date, number...) and if it is a word, it also has a part-of-speech tag (verb, noun, adverb...).

Since:
2/23/14
Author:
Ulflander
